14:10.371 --> 14:13.069
Well, it's nice
to see you, too, sis.

14:13.113 --> 14:15.767
JAMES: I'm gonna go see
what Sydney's up to.

14:15.811 --> 14:17.465
-Just...
-Mm.

14:17.508 --> 14:19.162
Yeah.

14:19.206 --> 14:21.338
This is not fair.

14:21.382 --> 14:23.558
I asked you not to come over.

14:23.601 --> 14:26.300
He knows where you live.
He will follow you.

14:26.343 --> 14:29.477
Yes, well, I have some news.

14:29.520 --> 14:31.261
