that justifies this.

14:31.305 --> 14:33.873
Okay, I have a plan,
and I just...

14:33.916 --> 14:35.962
I-I need you
to-to go along with it

14:36.005 --> 14:38.268
and just not be in control
for one second.

14:38.312 --> 14:40.880
