23:18.397 --> 23:19.789
CECILIA:
You're going to Parsons.

23:19.833 --> 23:21.443
-Oh, my God.

23:21.487 --> 23:22.923
Oh, wait, no.

23:22.966 --> 23:24.751
We got to cel...
we got to celebrate.

23:24.794 --> 23:27.406
And I don't want TV dinners,
microwave nothing, we...

23:27.449 --> 23:29.233
Oh, it's, like,
I guess too bad

