23:38.460 --> 23:40.201
-Yes, I can.
-CECILIA: Oh, come on.

23:40.244 --> 23:41.594
Just, like, a little bit.

23:41.637 --> 23:44.335
He said the other day that
I was mature for my age.

23:44.379 --> 23:45.467
-That's right.
-He did.

23:45.511 --> 23:46.773
-A mature child.
-I heard you say that.

23:46.816 --> 23:47.817
-I remember. -Hey,
hold up, hold up, hold up.

23:47.861 --> 23:49.079
This ain't fair, okay?
Two against one.

23:49.123 --> 23:50.472
I'm just an innocent man
trying to do right.

23:50.516 --> 23:51.517
Are you scared? Are you scared?

23:51.560 --> 23:52.779
This a... this is abuse.
I'm a cop.

23:52.822 --> 23:53.910
-Are you-you scared?
-You realize I'm a cop.

23:53.954 --> 23:55.738
-I got him, I got him.
-Hey, hey, hey.

23:57.914 --> 24:00.134
-I got him, Sydney! I got him!
-SYDNEY: No, he's got me!

24:02.658 --> 24:06.575
-Oh! I'll protect you!

25:30.572 --> 25:31.791
Morning.

25:31.834 --> 25:33.532
You want some breakfast?

25:33.575 --> 25:35.446
Nah, nah, I got to go.

25:35.490 --> 25:38.580
You know, I'm a little
hungover, believe it or not.

25:38.624 --> 25:40.887
Ugh. Me, too.

25:40.930 --> 25:43.846
Champagne does that to me
every time.

25:43.890 --> 25:45.761
-We're getting old, Cee.

25:45.805 --> 25:47.023
We old.

25:47.067 --> 25:48.677
These winter mornings
are killing me.

25:48.721 --> 25:50.505
All right, look,
I'm out of here.

25:50.549 --> 25:52.594
Um, I'll be back around 7:00.

25:52.638 --> 25:53.987
-Okay.
-All right?

25:54.030 --> 25:55.989
-Oh, uh, Cee.
-Hmm?

25:56.032 --> 25:57.860
You mind getting Sydney up?

25:57.904 --> 25:59.558
She's actually pretty excited,
thanks to you.

25:59.601 --> 26:02.648
She, uh... she might need
a little help staying focused.

26:02.691 --> 26:04.475
You got it.

26:13.659 --> 26:15.486
Syd, come on, girl.

26:15.530 --> 26:17.314
