On the sheets.

34:54.353 --> 34:56.050
I saw it right there.

34:56.094 --> 34:58.400
-I saw them.
-On the sheet?

34:58.444 --> 35:00.707
I saw it.

35:00.750 --> 35:04.058
There was someone in here.
There was someone in here.

35:04.102 --> 35:05.190
Syd, put that
stupid thing away.

35:05.233 --> 35:06.756
Y-You're the one
who bought it for me.

35:06.800 --> 35:08.410
Who you gonna spray? Who?

35:10.151 --> 35:12.240
James, I saw it.

35:13.198 --> 35:15.025
I swear.

35:15.069 --> 35:17.158
Hey, Cee.

35:19.247 --> 35:22.729
Adrian will haunt you
if you let him.

35:22.772 --> 35:24.557
Don't let him.

35:26.863 --> 35:29.475
Now, you should try
and get some sleep.

35:29.518 --> 35:31.912
You have an important
job interview tomorrow,

35:31.955 --> 35:34.262
and I don't want the memory
of this motherfu...

35:35.698 --> 35:37.961
...that...

35:38.005 --> 35:41.965
this person to ruin it.

35:42.009 --> 35:43.967
-Okay?
-Okay, yeah.

35:44.011 --> 35:45.708
-Sorry.
-Yeah.

